<body>
<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="11700000t" end="33900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">你们已经没有利用价值了</p>
<p begin="34300000t" end="52600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">看看上面吧 白痴</p>
<p begin="139400000t" end="160600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">艾连和克里斯塔在哪</p>
<p begin="172300000t" end="189400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">没用的</p>
<p begin="189400000t" end="206900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">你们不自首被抓的话</p>
<p begin="206900000t" end="238600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">调查兵就会被全员处刑</p>
<p begin="238600000t" end="265300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">我拜托皮克希斯司令一件事</p>
<p begin="265300000t" end="292900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">要是那个时刻来临的话… 届时 我只能旁观</p>
<p begin="292900000t" end="334200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">要做出选择的是你 还有他们…</p>
<p begin="1244700000t" end="1294790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">答复</p>
<p begin="1384400000t" end="1402700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">马车还真多</p>
<p begin="1416500000t" end="1429800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">到底怎么啦</p>
<p begin="1429800000t" end="1444400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">你不知道吗</p>
<p begin="1444800000t" end="1480300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">现在正集合所有兵团干部去城里</p>
<p begin="1480700000t" end="1509100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">进行解散调查军团的程序呢</p>
<p begin="1509500000t" end="1552000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">你看 那是执行那个团长死刑的处刑台</p>
<p begin="1557000000t" end="1590000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">现在应该正在执行最后的审判中吧</p>
<p begin="1600400000t" end="1657100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">失去调查军团亦即失去人类之矛</p>
<p begin="1661700000t" end="1693000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">不是在敌人逼近时守护自身的盾</p>
<p begin="1697600000t" end="1718900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">而是能够主动排除威胁的矛</p>
<p begin="1723900000t" end="1768100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">假设就在现在这个时刻敌人攻破罗塞之墙</p>
<p begin="1773500000t" end="1824400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">罗塞之墙的平民就会再度进入席纳之墙内避难</p>
<p begin="1828100000t" end="1881500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">因早先的避难行动 储粮已经见底撑不了几天</p>
<p begin="1887400000t" end="1909100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">用不了多久 几乎所有平民</p>
<p begin="1909100000t" end="1937800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">都会被迫为生存而抗争</p>
<p begin="1944900000t" end="1985000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">这意味着以罗塞之墙和席纳之墙为界</p>
<p begin="1985400000t" end="2010800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">分成两边的人类将开启内战</p>
<p begin="2017900000t" end="2041300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">就算墙壁没被攻破</p>
<p begin="2043400000t" end="2078000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">罗塞之墙区域内也已渐有粮食不足问题</p>
<p begin="2082100000t" end="2113000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">攻破席纳之墙的不是巨人</p>
<p begin="2117200000t" end="2163100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">而是罗塞之墙平民的可能性并非是零</p>
<p begin="2203500000t" end="2222300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">夺回玛利亚之墙</p>
<p begin="2225600000t" end="2269400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">走投无路的人类要开拓未来只有这个方法</p>
<p begin="2276100000t" end="2315300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">你想说为此调查军团是必要的</p>
<p begin="2317000000t" end="2362400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">领头杀入敌人阵地是我们调查军团的责任</p>
<p begin="2362800000t" end="2394500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">一味被动防守是解决不了任何问题的</p>
<p begin="2403700000t" end="2459200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">还是说各位有改变现况的妙计吗</p>
<p begin="2524700000t" end="2558000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">艾尔文 你似乎还没理解状况</p>
<p begin="2558500000t" end="2575500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">你之所以会在这里</p>
<p begin="2575500000t" end="2604300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">既不是为了讨论城墙的未来</p>
<p begin="2604800000t" end="2639000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">也不是只因为杀人这种单纯的犯罪</p>
<p begin="2645600000t" end="2664800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">而是因为根据人类宪章第六条</p>
<p begin="2664800000t" end="2711100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">“将个人利益置于人类续存之上”</p>
<p begin="2719000000t" end="2743200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">你严重违反此规条</p>
<p begin="2743200000t" end="2789100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">没错 多次拒绝交出艾连·叶卡</p>
<p begin="2789100000t" end="2821200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">已经完全违背人类宪章条款</p>
<p begin="2821200000t" end="2854200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">艾连是夺回码利亚之墙的关键</p>
<p begin="2854600000t" end="2878400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">做出决定的不是调查军团</p>
<p begin="2878400000t" end="2912600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">艾连·叶卡是拥有未知力量的巨人</p>
<p begin="2912600000t" end="2947600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">要让他待在墙内必须背负相当程度的风险</p>
<p begin="2947600000t" end="2993100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">怎么可能让区区一介军团长自行管理</p>
<p begin="2993100000t" end="3031000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">但你对自己的主张十分坚持</p>
<p begin="3031000000t" end="3076900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">自导自演诱使事件把艾连·叶卡藏起来</p>
<p begin="3077300000t" end="3108600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">还对迪墨·利布斯杀人灭口</p>
<p begin="3114400000t" end="3134000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">这已构成反叛</p>
<p begin="3134000000t" end="3176200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">现在你们才是人类真正的威胁啊</p>
<p begin="3185300000t" end="3199100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">皮克希斯司令</p>
<p begin="3209100000t" end="3254600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">驻扎军团和调查军团同在前线拼命</p>
<p begin="3254600000t" end="3288400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">据说关系相当密切是吧</p>
<p begin="3288800000t" end="3337600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">真遗憾您以为我们会与调查军团同一阵线</p>
<p begin="3338000000t" end="3371400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">没有什么比人类自相残杀更愚蠢的了</p>
<p begin="3374300000t" end="3402600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">一旦在这狭隘的人世点了火</p>
<p begin="3403100000t" end="3432200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">相信要不了多久就会化为一片焦土了吧</p>
<p begin="3438500000t" end="3468100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">先前托洛斯特区保卫战时</p>
<p begin="3468500000t" end="3488100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">我也这么教育士兵</p>
<p begin="3488100000t" end="3511900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">令他们自愿牺性奉献</p>
<p begin="3520700000t" end="3546900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">若是调查军团会成为火种</p>
<p begin="3546900000t" end="3567000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">那么就应该趁早捻熄吧</p>
<p begin="3577400000t" end="3637900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">毕竟被巨人攻破城墙之际要是没剩多少人</p>
<p begin="3638300000t" end="3662900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">我看巨人也会很失望吧</p>
<p begin="3684600000t" end="3717900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">很好 那么进行商议</p>
<p begin="3747100000t" end="3776300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">陛下 您看怎样</p>
<p begin="3858500000t" end="3889800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">艾尔文 你打算就这样结束吗</p>
<p begin="3980300000t" end="4020300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">那么以陛下之名宣布判决</p>
<p begin="4026600000t" end="4045800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">受刑人 艾尔文·史密斯</p>
<p begin="4045800000t" end="4100400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">以违反人类宪章第六条之罪处以死刑</p>
<p begin="4123400000t" end="4166300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">此判决即刻执行 带下去</p>
<p begin="4198400000t" end="4223900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">这样真的好吗 艾尔文</p>
<p begin="4291400000t" end="4310200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">你真的就…</p>
<p begin="4459500000t" end="4495000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">罗塞之墙被攻破了</p>
<p begin="4495000000t" end="4503300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">什…</p>
<p begin="4527900000t" end="4567500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">突然出现的超大型巨人和盔甲巨人</p>
<p begin="4567500000t" end="4594700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">破坏了卡拉涅斯区的两扇大门</p>
<p begin="4602200000t" end="4638900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">现在从东区方向有大量难民涌入</p>
<p begin="4652600000t" end="4672200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">确保避难路线</p>
<p begin="4677700000t" end="4721400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">驻扎军团前线部队全兵力在东区集合</p>
<p begin="4721400000t" end="4748100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">引导平民至席纳之墙避难</p>
<p begin="4748100000t" end="4784800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">快点行动 以平民避难为最优先事项</p>
<p begin="4784800000t" end="4794000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">是</p>
<p begin="4794000000t" end="4801900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">不准</p>
<p begin="4815700000t" end="4842400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">封闭席纳之墙全区大门</p>
<p begin="4842800000t" end="4871600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">不准让任何难民闯进来</p>
<p begin="4880400000t" end="4891200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">什…</p>
<p begin="4897500000t" end="4937500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">那 那是指要对罗塞之墙的平民</p>
<p begin="4944600000t" end="4980900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">对超过半数的人类见死不救的意思吗</p>
<p begin="4982500000t" end="5020900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">就跟刚才他说的一样只会引发内战</p>
<p begin="5020900000t" end="5047600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">有可能会瘫痪中央政府机能</p>
<p begin="5047600000t" end="5062200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">要真如此一切就完蛋了</p>
<p begin="5062200000t" end="5103500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">但 但是那也只是假设而已…</p>
<p begin="5103500000t" end="5128900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">重点在假设有可能成真</p>
<p begin="5128900000t" end="5161900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">我们可是有最高决定权的机关</p>
<p begin="5161900000t" end="5178600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">还不决点照做</p>
<p begin="5253600000t" end="5299500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">可恶 没想到城墙会在这种时候被攻破</p>
<p begin="5299500000t" end="5325400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">但也算是不幸中的大幸吧</p>
<p begin="5325400000t" end="5345400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">已经找到“力量”了</p>
<p begin="5348700000t" end="5389600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">只要撑到“容器”接受力量为止就好</p>
<p begin="5389600000t" end="5438400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">没错 现在不是为眼前的损失慌乱的时候</p>
<p begin="5438400000t" end="5469300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">只要还有席纳之墙总有办法的</p>
<p begin="5469300000t" end="5495600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">啊啊 只要雷斯卿回来就…</p>
<p begin="5518100000t" end="5541900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">只能做了 去把门堵上</p>
<p begin="5542300000t" end="5551900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">慢着</p>
<p begin="5551900000t" end="5568500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">再等就来不及了</p>
<p begin="5595700000t" end="5614800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">做出选择的会是谁</p>
<p begin="5614800000t" end="5632800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">谁来决定</p>
<p begin="5632800000t" end="5658200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">还愣着干什么快点行动</p>
<p begin="5658200000t" end="5681200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">是想背叛王政府吗</p>
<p begin="5707900000t" end="5719900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">我做不到</p>
<p begin="5720800000t" end="5729100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">什么</p>
<p begin="5742100000t" end="5772100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">我是罗塞之墙的居民</p>
<p begin="5782500000t" end="5805400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">我要阻止大门封锁</p>
<p begin="5805400000t" end="5815000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">你这家伙</p>
<p begin="5815000000t" end="5832600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">也算上我吧</p>
<p begin="5832600000t" end="5839200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">什</p>
<p begin="5893500000t" end="5918500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">达里斯·萨克雷</p>
<p begin="5929300000t" end="5956000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">听到他们的判断您是否感到意外</p>
<p begin="5956000000t" end="5971900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">萨克雷总统</p>
<p begin="5982300000t" end="6005200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">不 完全没有</p>
<p begin="6005600000t" end="6031900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">萨克雷 这到底</p>
<p begin="6039400000t" end="6082000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">方才的通报是误报 请安心</p>
<p begin="6085700000t" end="6125800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">现在并没有确认到任何巨人来袭的情报</p>
<p begin="6125800000t" end="6155000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">什…你这家伙这是想干什么</p>
<p begin="6155000000t" end="6184600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">主谋者是我</p>
<p begin="6184600000t" end="6197500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">皮克希斯</p>
<p begin="6202500000t" end="6246300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">中央宪兵大半都去了别的地方呢</p>
<p begin="6246300000t" end="6268800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">该说是走运吗…</p>
<p begin="6268800000t" end="6282200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">到底怎么回事</p>
<p begin="6282200000t" end="6341800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">方才我说驻扎军团与调查军团无联手之事</p>
<p begin="6345600000t" end="6368900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">可我忘了多说这一句</p>
<p begin="6375200000t" end="6402300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">我们可也没和你们站同一阵线</p>
<p begin="6410600000t" end="6450300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">虽说我也与艾尔文有一样的想怯</p>
<p begin="6454800000t" end="6486100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">但也曾犹豫是否将一切交给你们政府</p>
