<p begin="6529500000t" end="6581200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">因为你们大概比我们更加了解墙壁和巨人</p>
<p begin="6593300000t" end="6639600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">想着如果只有你们才能挽救更多人类</p>
