<p begin="6797700000t" end="6840200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">即便对巨人的力量和来龙去脉一无所知</p>
<p begin="6840200000t" end="6889400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">我们仍能比你们令更多生命续存</p>
<p begin="6889400000t" end="6906500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">别 别说傻话了</p>
<p begin="6906500000t" end="6933200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">就算镇压了这里那又怎么样</p>
<p begin="6933700000t" end="6961200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">你以为民众会服从吗</p>
<p begin="6961200000t" end="6991200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">民众只会臣服于王</p>
