<p begin="7015000000t" end="7042500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">看样子你还没理解状况呢</p>
<p begin="7048400000t" end="7088800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">这不是威胁 是政变</p>
