<p begin="7203100000t" end="7240600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">有时比起国王更会优先遵从长官</p>
<p begin="7240600000t" end="7269800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">既然这国王是假的就更不用说了</p>
<p begin="7269800000t" end="7296500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">我们打算拥立真正的王</p>
<p begin="7303600000t" end="7328600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">怎么会…居然打算做到这个地步</p>
<p begin="7337800000t" end="7369900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">你以为这跟诈欺没两样的手段真行得通吗</p>
