<p begin="7416200000t" end="7440400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">才真的是违反人类宪章第六条</p>
<p begin="7440400000t" end="7449200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">什…</p>
<p begin="7449200000t" end="7496300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">再加上拥立伪王独自揽政之罪</p>
<p begin="7496300000t" end="7516300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">足以判处极刑</p>
<p begin="7590600000t" end="7611800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">可恶你给我起来 臭老头</p>
<p begin="7611800000t" end="7626400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">怎么吃饭了吗</p>
