<p begin="7763200000t" end="7777800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">你不高兴吗</p>
<p begin="7792900000t" end="7801200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">奈尔</p>
<p begin="7810800000t" end="7861300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">人类不得不走上更艰难的荆棘之路了</p>
<p begin="8050200000t" end="8081500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">如信所述 政变成功了</p>
<p begin="8084800000t" end="8125300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">王都和行政区都由萨克雷总统临时接收</p>
<p begin="8129000000t" end="8164100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">目前还没有传出贵族叛乱的消息</p>
<p begin="8164500000t" end="8190300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">但是 那利布斯会长的事件呢</p>
<p begin="8193300000t" end="8223300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">因为有证言说是冤罪</p>
<p begin="8225400000t" end="8252100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">会长儿子的弗雷格尔正在努力呢</p>
<p begin="8252100000t" end="8271700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">你还不懂嘛</p>
<p begin="8271700000t" end="8303400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">王政府的家伙们根本没打算救我们啊</p>
<p begin="8304200000t" end="8317100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">现在假装没看见</p>
<p begin="8317100000t" end="8336300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">等真的被杀就来不及了啊</p>
<p begin="8336300000t" end="8349200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">就是啊</p>
<p begin="8349200000t" end="8390500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">下次再被巨人攻击就什么都不剩了</p>
<p begin="8392600000t" end="8415100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">不管是公司还是家人</p>
<p begin="8419700000t" end="8448500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">在那之前把真相写出来吧</p>
<p begin="8463500000t" end="8484000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">就跟这上面写的一样</p>
<p begin="8484000000t" end="8518600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">把枉加冤罪 王政府施加的压力</p>
<p begin="8518600000t" end="8549400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">弗利玆王其实是伪王都写清楚了</p>
<p begin="8553600000t" end="8586600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">关于你们的事情也证明是正当防卫</p>
<p begin="8589900000t" end="8625400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">也就是说 我们现在都是自由身了</p>
<p begin="8662900000t" end="8697900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">太棒了</p>
<p begin="8704600000t" end="8733800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">怎么会这样…</p>
<p begin="8739200000t" end="8759700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">还真是夸张的豪赌呢</p>
<p begin="8777200000t" end="8799700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">不过不只是艾尔文他们</p>
<p begin="8803400000t" end="8841400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">是每个人的选择 一起改变了世界</p>
<p begin="8867700000t" end="8899800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">我害你托付给我的三位队员枉死了</p>
<p begin="8909400000t" end="8920200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">抱歉…</p>
<p begin="8953600000t" end="8986100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">一部分的中央宪兵和宪兵的头头</p>
<p begin="8986100000t" end="9021200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">艾连和希丝特莉亚都还在不知道在哪</p>
<p begin="9021200000t" end="9038700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">得决点找出来才行</p>
<p begin="9055400000t" end="9073300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">那件事我有线索</p>
<p begin="9084600000t" end="9117100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">让这场战斗在那里画下句点吧</p>
<p begin="9124700000t" end="9174800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">现在可以公开情报</p>
