<p begin="9124700000t" end="9174800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"></p>
<p begin="9124700000t" end="9174800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"></p>
<p begin="9124700000t" end="9174800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"></p>
<p begin="9193000000t" end="9219300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">公开宣布因艾尔文的行动</p>
<p begin="9219300000t" end="9253900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">现有体制已崩坏的事实</p>
<p begin="9261000000t" end="9316900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">这是在兵团组织压制王都与行政区后</p>
<p begin="9316900000t" end="9370700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">立刻在为了他所准备的处刑台上发表的</p>
<p begin="9375700000t" end="9389400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">正是如此</p>
<p begin="9389400000t" end="9422400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">正如方才萨克雷总统的宣言</p>
<p begin="9422800000t" end="9465400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">我们的目的不在以兵团组织进行统治</p>
<p begin="9465800000t" end="9505400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">将由真正的王家取代弗利兹家拥立新王</p>
<p begin="9505800000t" end="9538300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">担任引导民众的明灯</p>
<p begin="9538800000t" end="9557100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">这我了解</p>
<p begin="9560000000t" end="9605100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">但民众真会那么轻易接纳新王吗</p>
<p begin="9605500000t" end="9637600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">事实上确实有许多人都很不安</p>
<p begin="9640500000t" end="9667600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">不知道今后该相信什么</p>
<p begin="9688100000t" end="9708100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">若是为了人类着想</p>
<p begin="9712700000t" end="9739400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">应该要照旧将一切托付给王政府</p>
<p begin="9748600000t" end="9768600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">正如皮克希斯司令所言</p>
<p begin="9769000000t" end="9811500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">他们令人类在巨人威胁下生存的手段就是</p>
<p begin="9814900000t" end="9844900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">就算对半数人类见死不救</p>
<p begin="9845300000t" end="9871200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">也比全人类灭绝来得好</p>
<p begin="9897900000t" end="9915800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">我本该交出艾连</p>
<p begin="9915800000t" end="9962100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">连同同伴和自己的性命一起放弃责任</p>
<p begin="9962100000t" end="9989200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">将一切托付给王政</p>
<p begin="9989600000t" end="10029700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">如果说与个人比起来 人类更加尊贵的话</p>
<p begin="10068000000t" end="10099300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">你的使命还是如此艰辛</p>
<p begin="10102200000t" end="10128900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">看样子死了反而是种解脱</p>
<p begin="10148100000t" end="10183200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">但 如果是这样你为何不那么做</p>
<p begin="10190700000t" end="10202300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">那是因为…</p>
<p begin="10202300000t" end="10223600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">要说说我的理由吗</p>
<p begin="10231500000t" end="10265300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">因为我从以前就看那些家伙不爽</p>
<p begin="10268690000t" end="10286600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">令人火大啊</p>
<p begin="10286600000t" end="10321600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">一脸跩样的家伙和明明不伟大却居上位的家伙</p>
<p begin="10322500000t" end="10355790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">不 不如说是因为我喜欢吧</p>
<p begin="10356190000t" end="10391700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">仔细想想我一直都期待有这一天呢</p>
<p begin="10391700000t" end="10416300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">也就是说即使你没动手</p>
<p begin="10416300000t" end="10452200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">我也打算在死前给他们一点颜色瞧瞧</p>
<p begin="10452600000t" end="10502600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">这场政变对人类是好是坏我一点兴趣也没有</p>
<p begin="10512200000t" end="10534300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">我真是个大坏蛋呢</p>
<p begin="10541800000t" end="10567700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">但说起这个 你也是一样吧</p>
<p begin="10580600000t" end="10607300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">你其实是不想死的</p>
<p begin="10612300000t" end="10666600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">和我一样 比起人类的命运选择了个人</p>
<p begin="10677800000t" end="10715400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">我似乎太骄傲自大了…</p>
<p begin="10719100000t" end="10742500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">你的理由是什么</p>
<p begin="10746200000t" end="10772900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">该轮你回答了</p>
<p begin="10797900000t" end="10833800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">其实我有个梦想</p>
<p begin="10844600000t" end="10866800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">是从小就有的梦想</p>
<p begin="10977300000t" end="10988500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">汉吉分队长</p>
<p begin="10992300000t" end="11013200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">你说有两人所在之处的线索是…</p>
<p begin="11020700000t" end="11035300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">我接下来就说明</p>
<p begin="11041500000t" end="11084900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">这是艾尔文交给我的雷斯卿领地的调查报告</p>
<p begin="11084900000t" end="11107000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">内容几乎都是关于五年前</p>
<p begin="11107800000t" end="11136600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">袭击雷斯家的那个事件</p>
<p begin="11137400000t" end="11149500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">五年前</p>
<p begin="11149500000t" end="11182900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">没错 就是玛利亚之墙被破坏的那天</p>
<p begin="11191200000t" end="11223400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">总之 我从头概略说明起</p>
<p begin="11223800000t" end="11278400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">罗德·雷斯这个男人作为领主的评价并不差</p>
<p begin="11282600000t" end="11303000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">膝下有五个孩子</p>
<p begin="11303000000t" end="11362200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">别是长女芙莉妲个性随和颇受领民喜爱</p>
<p begin="11372700000t" end="11404800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">但在五年前的夜晚 发生一场悲剧</p>
<p begin="11410600000t" end="11445200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">盗贼趁着情势正混乱时袭击领地</p>
<p begin="11445200000t" end="11482800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">烧毁了村里唯一一座礼拜堂</p>
<p begin="11492000000t" end="11547400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">可怜的是那天晚上雷斯一家都在那梼告</p>
<p begin="11554500000t" end="11607500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">除了当家罗德·雷斯以外的家族成员</p>
<p begin="11613800000t" end="11645400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">全都惨遭盗贼杀害了</p>
<p begin="11669200000t" end="11741000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">这是在希丝特莉亚的母亲被中央宪兵杀害前几天发生的事</p>
<p begin="11761000000t" end="11791800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">也就是说罗德·雷斯在失去家人后</p>
<p begin="11791800000t" end="11815600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">就立刻主动接触希丝特莉亚</p>
<p begin="11820200000t" end="11861500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">从中可看出他们需要希丝特莉亚的理由</p>
<p begin="11869000000t" end="11888200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">血缘关系吗…</p>
<p begin="11891900000t" end="11919100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">你是想说关键在于血统吗</p>
<p begin="11919100000t" end="11939900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">这个部分现在还不清楚</p>
<p begin="11939900000t" end="11963300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">比起那个我在意的是</p>
<p begin="11964500000t" end="11992000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">礼拜堂被全部烧毁这件事</p>
<p begin="11992500000t" end="12014600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">礼拜堂是石造建筑</p>
<p begin="12014600000t" end="12048800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">要破坏掉需要花费相当的时间跟力气</p>
<p begin="12052500000t" end="12085100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">真是盗贼的话 应该会偷完就立刻逃跑才对</p>
<p begin="12085100000t" end="12128400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">而且看见盗贼的只有罗德·雷斯一人</p>
<p begin="12137200000t" end="12181000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">之后他动用私产重建了礼拜堂</p>
<p begin="12181000000t" end="12194700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">是为了什么呢</p>
<p begin="12240200000t" end="12296100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">不如说这里不可能和巨人无关</p>
<p begin="12296500000t" end="12323200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">就算只是我的贸然推测</p>
<p begin="12323600000t" end="12373300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">但可疑到这个程度 已值得去一探究竟了</p>
<p begin="12613500000t" end="12626000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">怎么回事</p>
<p begin="12726100000t" end="12742800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">等天一亮</p>
<p begin="12742800000t" end="12769900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">兵团就会进到雷斯领地</p>
<p begin="12776200000t" end="12812000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">雷斯应该不会好心等到那时候吧</p>
<p begin="12820000000t" end="12842900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">我们不赶快过去的话</p>
<p begin="12842900000t" end="12867900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">艾连说不定会被吃掉</p>
<p begin="12897100000t" end="12918800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">能巨人化的人类</p>
<p begin="12918800000t" end="12955100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">可以借由吃掉巨人来继承能力</p>
<p begin="12960100000t" end="12985500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">如果这是真的…</p>
<p begin="12989700000t" end="13028900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">艾连是什么时候 怎么变成巨人</p>
<p begin="13028900000t" end="13054800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">吃掉了谁才获得能力的呢…</p>
<p begin="13122800000t" end="13133600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">可恶…</p>
<p begin="13250400000t" end="13267100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">希丝特莉亚…</p>
<p begin="13330200000t" end="13430300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">大地と大空は 何故別れたのだろう</p>
<p begin="13434100000t" end="13538400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">世界は残酷で されど美しい</p>
<p begin="13544400000t" end="13595200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">石を投げる者と 投げられる者には</p>
<p begin="13596200000t" end="13644800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">容易に越えられぬ 柵がある</p>
<p begin="13649800000t" end="13699000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">立ち位置が替われば 正義は牙を剥く</p>
<p begin="13702200000t" end="13755600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">檻の中で吼えているのは 果たしてどちらか</p>
<p begin="13758900000t" end="13825400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">心臓を捧げた 戻せない黄昏に</p>
<p begin="13827600000t" end="13900300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">進み続けた夜の果て 楽園は何処にある？</p>
<p begin="13912200000t" end="13951400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">Requiem Requiem</p>
<p begin="13954200000t" end="13986000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">この夜に散った名も無き花よ</p>
<p begin="13987100000t" end="14069200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">どうか安らかに暁に眠れ</p>
<p begin="14210900000t" end="14228900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">为了救出艾连</p>
<p begin="14228900000t" end="14254700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">米卡莎等人朝着礼拜堂前进</p>
<p begin="14257200000t" end="14286800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">但被拘束的艾连得知了</p>
<p begin="14286800000t" end="14327700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">父亲古利夏不可原谅的罪孽</p>
<p begin="14337100000t" end="14353300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">下一回“罪孽”</p>
</div>
